0 'ilb' prints
    1 ilb 0 assert_eq
    16 ilb 4 assert_eq
    1024 ilb 10 assert_eq
    65536 ilb 16 assert_eq
    123456789 ilb 26 assert_eq
    120 ! ilb 660 assert_eq
    52656145834278593348959013841835216159447547700274555627155488768 ilb 215 assert_eq
OK

0 'ilog' prints
